OL,5,FRobbie Hall, Age: 100, Women's
OL,6,FAuxiliary Air Force
OL,8,FInterviewed 1 November 2023
OL,10,FLying about her age to become a WAAF
OL,11,Fwhen she was just 17, Robbie Hall
OL,12,Fworked for the accounts section of RAF
OL,13,FBomber Command, keeping Air Ministry
OL,14,Fregulations and instructions up to
OL,15,Fdate.
OL,17,FHer boss was Sir Arthur "Bomber"
OL,18,FHarris, who's plan to bomb Nazi
OL,19,FGermany into submission by reducing
OL,20,Fits industrial cities to rubble
OL,21,Fremains controversial.
