OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Robbie Hall
OL,5,F"They sent me home that day because
OL,6,Fobviously I was upset and it was
OL,7,Fdifficult living in the same house as
OL,8,Fhis parents.
OL,10,F"If you stopped to think about it
OL,11,Fwhich I've done in later years, he was
OL,12,Fshot down. Did his plane burst into
OL,13,Fflames? Because they used to try for
OL,14,Fthe petrol tanks.
OL,16,F"Did he get burnt alive in the plane
OL,17,Fas it came down? Did he get killed on
OL,18,Fimpact? Did it burst into flame on
OL,19,Fimpact? What did they find of him?
