OL,5,F"Because his parents went out - I
OL,6,Fwouldn't go - to see the gravestones
OL,7,Fand there were four names on that
OL,8,Fmemorial.
OL,10,F"We were both 21. And at my age I
OL,11,Fthink 'How young we were. What did we
OL,12,Fknow? We hadn't lived.'"
